OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777903640
OL,3,CAlmost #600,000 secured to target
OL,4,Cknife crime hotspots
OL,6,FAlmost #600,000 will go towards
OL,7,Ftargeting knife crime hotspots in
OL,8,FSussex.
OL,10,FThe funding from the Home Office's
OL,11,FKnife Crime Concentration Fund (KCCF)
OL,12,Fwill help to expand efforts to reduce
OL,13,Fincidents in "high-harm locations".
OL,15,FFour areas have been identified in
OL,16,FSussex - two in Brighton and one in
OL,17,FEastbourne and Crawley.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
