OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777903640
OL,3,CAlmost #600,000 secured to target
OL,4,Cknife crime hotspots
OL,6,FOfficers will analyse the crime in
OL,7,Fthese locations to understand the
OL,8,Funderlying factors that cause the
OL,9,Fconcentrated criminality.
OL,11,FThe #594,909 will go towards
OL,12,Fdelivering local intervention plans
OL,13,Ffor each area, with agreed initiatives
OL,14,Flaunching by September.
OL,16,FOver the past year, there has been a
OL,17,F24.6% reduction in crime involving
OL,18,Fknives across the county.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
