OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777903640
OL,3,CAlmost #600,000 secured to target
OL,4,Cknife crime hotspots
OL,6,FSussex Police and Crime Commissioner
OL,7,F(PCC) Katy Bourne has welcomed the
OL,8,Ffunding announcement, adding it will
OL,9,Fbuild on the force's efforts.
OL,11,FShe said: "Hotspot policing patrols
OL,12,Fhave already delivered clear and
OL,13,Fmeasurable results, playing a vital
OL,14,Frole in reducing crime while providing
OL,15,Fresidents with a strong, visible
OL,16,Fpolice presence.
OL,18,F"This proactive approach has sent a
OL,19,Fclear message that criminal activity
OL,20,Fwill not be tolerated and acts as a
OL,21,Fpowerful deterrent.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777903640
OL,3,CAlmost #600,000 secured to target
OL,4,Cknife crime hotspots
OL,6,F"Sadly, recent events in Brighton
OL,7,Fremind us how quickly lives can be
OL,8,Fimpacted when someone chooses to carry
OL,9,Fa knife.
OL,11,F"I have worked closely with Sussex
OL,12,FPolice to secure investment from the
OL,13,FKnife Crime Concentration Fund and I
OL,14,Fam delighted that our bid has been
OL,15,Fsuccessful.
OL,17,F"This funding will enable the force to
OL,18,Fexpand its proven hotspot policing
OL,19,Fmodel, adopting a targeted, local
OL,20,Fapproach in the areas where knife
OL,21,Fcrime is most prevalent.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777903640
OL,3,CAlmost #600,000 secured to target
OL,4,Cknife crime hotspots
OL,6,F"I'm particularly encouraged that this
OL,7,Ffunding will also enable us to retain
OL,8,Fthe Night Safety Marshals in Brighton,
OL,9,Fhelping to reduce knife enabled
OL,10,Fviolence and keep people safe during
OL,11,Fnights out.
OL,13,F"While Sussex continues to experience
OL,14,Fknife crime levels below the national
OL,15,Faverage, we cannot be complacent. I
OL,16,Flook forward to seeing the impact this
OL,17,Ftargeted investment will deliver."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
